ence to detect and prevent fraud electronic billing reconciliation and operational risk management capabilities kight who continued to serve through march  as vice chairman of fiserv following checkfree’s acquisition holds more than a dozen patents for electronic banking and payment systems “i am delighted to join huntington which has been at the forefront of innovative banking and community programs” said kight “i look forward to being part of an active board that is committed to increasing shareholder value and its communities as we grow the bank” if you liked this article you might like winners and losers of the feds  bank stress tests the banks are expected in aggregate to increase their distributions to nearly  of their net earnings over the next four quarters however some did better than others ronald orol jul    am edt heres how to play new fed stress tests on the  biggest us banks the second piece of the annual reviews determines how much banks can spend on dividends and stock buybacks ronald orol jun    am edt midcap bank ma could surge as gop looks to overhaul financial regulations the gulf between the republican wish list on financial regulations and the legislative reality is large emily stewart jun    pm edt heres why midsized bank stocks could get a boost the possibility of legislative relief for regional banks came up at a hearing thursday ronald orol jun    pm edt trending  reasons dying sears had to strike a deal with the ruthless amazon amazon deceptive pricing probe by the ftc could be the start of a government siege dont sleep on general electrics cheap stock price sears just surrendered to amazon with kenmore deal amazon is catching heat in washington on  things related to its whole foods deal advertising partners  thestreet inc all rights reservedaction alerts plus is a registered trademark of thestreet inc compare brokers peter j kight executive profile  biography  bloomberg july    am et software company overview of mx technologies inc snapsh